[17/09/2019 21:12:27] <font color="#00ff00">"Lo he vendido"</font>
[17/09/2019 21:12:31] <font color="#00ff00">en dos duas y he ganado 2000 $.</font>
[17/09/2019 21:12:31] <font color="#00ff00">Un gran negocio para Gas Monkey.</font>
[17/09/2019 21:12:35] <font color="#00ff00">Vale, pásame eso.</font>
